==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frisian
<hw>Fri"sian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
Friesland, a province of the Netherlands; Friesic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frisian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Frisian
<hw>Fri"sian</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Friesland; also, the language spoken in Friesland. See <er>Friesic</er>,
<pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frisk</ent>⟦br⟧
